data.description: Welcome to kokomo way one of the biggest lots in the community. This newly updated home is ready for your family to move in. When you walk into the home you see the beautiful fireplace and spacious family room ready for your family get together's. The family room branches off into to the kitchen and dining area where there is tons of space. With 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths you have all the space you need in this home. It is the second biggest lot in the neighborhood so you know there is plenty of room for the family barn fire. It is right of i85 exit 14 that's less then 30 minutes to Anderson and less then 15 to Clemson. The lake is only 5 minutes away!!  You have to come see it for yourself! Hurry this home won't last long. Pendleton Schools. This home is sold as is
